Hi Tim,
More than likely you will have a chunk of your bus rip off from that hitch.

The area you have it bolted to is only sheet metal and will soon fatigue
from 
pulling that kind of load.  You really need to U-bolt the hitch to the rear 
torsion bar tubes to have enough strength!!!
Eric&Barb
